column2: rhat <- ggplot(data=fit.salcha$daily, aes(x=date)) + geom_point(aes(y=GPP_Rhat, colour = "GPP")) + geom_point(aes(y=as.numeric(ER_Rhat), colour = "ER")) + geom_point(aes(y=K600_daily_Rhat, colour = "K600")) +
labs(y = "RHAT") + theme(legend.position="top") + theme(axis.text.x=element_blank(), axis.ticks.x=element_blank(), axis.title.x=element_blank() )+ geom_hline(yintercept=20, color = "dark blue")
